  - Discernment-Truth=Reality=The Nature of Reality
By: Srî Sankarâchârya
---
The Yogi, whose intellect is perfect, contemplates all things as abiding in
himself and thus, by the eye of Knowledge (Jnâna-chakshus), he perceives
that everything is Âtmâ.
